Formed in 2003, EYMU is a french post-punk/deathrock band. Debut album "First Dinner" was released in 2005. The new album, called "Things As They Should Be" was released in 2008. EYMU played with bands such as C.D.1334, Cinema Strange, Chants Of Maldoror, Scary Bitches, The Vanishing, The 16s, All Gone Dead, Skeletal Family, and many others...
